Sass.mode
http://github.com/Brajeshwar/Sass.mode
----------------------------------------------

COMPATIBILITY

Coda - http://www.panic.com/coda/
SubEthaEdit - http://www.codingmonkeys.de/subethaedit/ (not tested, let me know if you test it)

SUPPORTED EXTENSIONS

.scss, .sass

INSTALL

1. Go to ~/Library/Application Support/Coda/Modes (create folder if needed)
2. Git Clone (or Copy) the "Sass.mode" folder

Alternate INSTALL

1. /Applications/Coda.app/Contents/Resources/Modes
2. Git Clone (or Copy) the "Sass.mode" folder

Note: In the Step 1 of Alternate INSTALL, you'll need to do a "Show Package Content" on the "Coda" Application

REFERENCES

More about Mode Customization: http://www.codingmonkeys.de/subethaedit/mode.html
Forked from an earlier project at http://upstruct.svn.beanstalkapp.com/sass/ (not mine)